'''Nasib Farah''' (yavutse 1981), ni  umunyasomaliya uba muri [[Danimarike|danimarke]] .  Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime zizwi cyane My COUSIN  PIRATE ,''Warrior from the North'' and ''Lost warrior'' .  Usibye gukora amafilime, ni umunyamakuru, umusemuzi, umuyobozi ushinzwe umusaruro, umufasha wigisha akaba n'umugiraneza.<ref>https://www.dfi.dk/en/viden-om-film/filmdatabasen/person/nasib-farah</ref><ref>http://www.filme-aus-afrika.de/EN/film-database/persons/personen-details/w/3591/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye muri [[Somaliya]] mu 1981. Mu 1990 yahunze [[Mogadishu]] n'umuryango we nyuma y'intambara yo muri [[Somaliya]].<ref>https://www.giffonifilmfestival.it/en/sezioni-film-2015/1185-warriors-from-the-north.html</ref> Icyakora, yabuze umuryango we igihe yarokoka hanyuma ahungira ku mupaka yerekeza muri [[Etiyopiya]], mbere yo guhaguruka mu [[Budage]] arangije atura muri [[Danimarike]].<ref>http://zagrebdox.net/en/2015/program/special_programme/middleast/warriors_from_the_north</ref>  Ku ikubitiro yari impunzi itaraherekejwe nyuma akurira mu kigo cya Croix Rouge cyo muri [[Danemarike]] Avnstrup hafi ya Lejre. 

Yashakanye n’umugore wo muri [[Danemarke]], babyarana abana.<ref>https://m.famousfix.com/list/danish-documentary-film-directors</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Yatoje nk'umucuruzi kandi akora nk'umunyamakuru wigenga imyaka mike. Nyuma yaje gushinga umuryango udaharanira inyungu wibanda ku gufasha abandi basore bo muri [[Somaliya]] binyuze mu kwigisha no nyuma y’ishuri<ref>https://www.aljazeera.com/features/2018/9/11/telling-the-stories-of-somalias-lost-warriors</ref>. Yifashishije iryo shyirahamwe kugira ngo agaragaze ibyamubayeho, Farah yatangije gahunda ya tereviziyo y'abaturage yitwa 'Qaran TV' ku baturage ba [[Somaliya]] muri [[Danimarike]].<ref>https://www.goethe.de/ins/ts/en/m/ver.cfm?date_start=%7Bts+%272016-04-01+00%3A00%3A00%27%7D&fuseaction=events.displayoutputtype&date_end=%7Bts+%272016-04-30+23%3A59%3A59%27%7D&</ref> 

Mu mwaka wa 2010, Farah yagize uruhare runini muri filime My COUSIN  PIRATE, iyobowe na Christian Sønderby Jepsen<ref>https://search.alexanderstreet.com/view/work/bibliographic_entity%7Cvideo_work%7C1795815/my-cousin-pirate</ref>. Icyakora buri gihe yakeneraga gukora nk'umuyobozi aho kuba umukinnyi.<ref>https://www.owlapps.net/owlapps_apps/articles?id=65634006&lang=en</ref> 

Muri 2015, yakoze ''filime yambere ya Warriors kuva mumajyaruguru'' . Yamamaye cyane kandi yerekanwa mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime.  Muri 2018, yayoboye documentaire ya kabiri ''Lost Warrior ari'' kumwe n'umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Danemarike]] Søren Steen Jespersen<ref>https://www.radiotimes.com/movie-guide/b-2pmce0/my-cousing-the-pirate/</ref><ref>https://www.giffonifilmfestival.it/en/sezioni-film-2015/1185-warriors-from-the-north.html</ref>

